ress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/msi-project-zero-x-ces-2025-front-side-angle.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1404\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"MSI Project Zero X\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/msi-project-zero-x-ces-2025-front-side-angle.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/msi-project-zero-x-ces-2025-front-side-angle.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/ideas-to-build-pc-that-stands-out/\" title=\"5 ideas to build a PC that stands out without going overboard\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t5 ideas to build a PC that stands out without going overboard\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eCrafting a PC with a unique aesthetic might have become harder, but it\u0026#39;s not impossible\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"modern-pc-cases-mean-many-common-mods-are-unnecessary\"\u003e\n                        Modern PC cases mean many common mods are unnecessary\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"improved-designs-and-