                 \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2400\" height=\"1598\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"cable sleeving tools and supplies on a desktop\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/cable-sleeving-tools.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBut then something changed two decades ago when \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/20th-anniversary-of-half-life-2/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eHalf-Life 2\u003c/em\u003e launched\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/steam-changed-pc-gaming-forever/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSteam changed how we bought PC games\u003c/a\u003e. With fewer titles being launched with physical discs, case manufacturers stopped including 5.25\u0026#34; bays, and then SSDs became more affordable, so fewer 3.5\u0026#34; HDD bays were included.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eCase manufacturers were keen users on the forums that PC modders congregated on to watch for trends and see which mods they could incorporate into future designs. PC cases with side windows and all-glass constructions wouldn\u0026#39;t exist without the PC modding community showing that they had a market. It\u0026#39;s possible that the ARGB LED lighting in most cases and components wouldn\u0026#39;t exist without modders playing with lighting.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"a595-4bbd-acf2be6301e0\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/ways-pc-case-manufactures-have-innovated/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An image showing the Antec P20C ARGB PC case kept on a table with a GPU and CPU retail next to it.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/01/antec-p20c-argb-pc-case-featured.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/ways-pc-case-manufactures-have-innovated/\" title=\"4 ways manufacturers innovated to create the modern PC case\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t4 ways manufacturers innovated to create the modern PC case\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eWe look back at all the times PC case makers innovated in the competitive space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"pc-modding-has-moved-on-to-different-things\"\u003e\n            PC modding has moved on to different things\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: eBay\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Old pc case\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/old-vintage-pc-case.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eSource: eBay\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen the hobby first started, it was a way to hack features (often literally) into old cases. When every case was a beige or black monolith with no airflow, every modder started by cutting holes in the front and sides of their case to add fans, windows, and cold cathode lighting tubes. Modern PC cases have included most, if not all, of the conveniences that PC modders used to create, from cable management to better airflow.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe landscape still has plenty of modders and competitions, but the bar to entry for competitive modding is also higher, as everyone is using CNC\u0026#39;ed parts and other advanced manufacturing techniques to create scratch builds, which use as little of the original PC case as possible, or in many cases, use none of it.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"5734-4ebb-9181078b5e22\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-to-pick-pc-case/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"How to pick a PC case\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/How-to-pick-a-PC-case.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-to-pick-pc-case/\" title=\"How to pick a PC case: 5 things to consider while buying a chassis for your build\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tHow to pick a PC case: 5 things to consider while buying a chassis for your build\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe PC case is the first and the most important thing to consider while building a PC. Here\u0026#39;s how to pick a PC case for your next build.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n               